						<br /><i>This might sound like I'm suggesting you need to do some big, up front schema design – but that's not true.<i><br /><br />I disagree, this is something you should be doing!  Remember your app will probably not be the only thing accessing the data.  Having a well-designed schema will help not just your app, but all other apps that will come along that need access to this data.<br /></i></i>
